    "abstract": "This poster reports on the usability and acceptance of a multimodal, interactive system for digitally capturing patient-reported outcomes among children and adolescents. Through iterative testing in pediatric contexts, we evaluate age-appropriate interaction (voice, touch, avatar guidance), comprehension, engagement, and burden. Insights translate into design recommendations for inclusive PROM workflows in child and adolescent medicine.",
